{
  "stem": "18932.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 449.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And me and my mom got the lower bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] The barrack was small, but there was a lot of barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was two big ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a number of small one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once-- ours was a small one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed in this barrack with, with those 16 other women, which, fortunately, quite a number of them are still alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we used to be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the war, we're still in contact with my friends, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were together, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I also forgot to tell you-- while in Auschwitz, when we had to go to the bathroom, we were all staying in groups of five.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't go to the bathroom when you wanted to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's when they told you have to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if somebody was in the middle or nothing and they said, this is finished, they had to get out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I also forget to tell you yet-- and this was this one day in that Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we came with my mom, we were staying in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this one kapo saw my mother with a cane.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she grabbed the cane.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she says, I'll be-- you'll be better off without it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She grabbed the cane.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And unfortunately, she, she broke this cane on another poor woman's back when she couldn't hold-- she had diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was just unbelievable what we went through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, you can't imagine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camps?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we got, I think, one soup-- a thin soup once a day, I remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the working camp, we also got a bread for, for the 16 women--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, every morning, they would send us in trains to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had to run to catch the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
